# CPDSS Interview Examples

### Total records in communication table

```sql
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM data_transfer_in_bound;
```

---

### Latest vessel communication count

```sql
SELECT vessel_id,
       COUNT(*)
FROM data_transfer_in_bound
GROUP BY vessel_id;
```

---

### Maximum communication delay

```sql
SELECT MAX(processed_time)
FROM data_transfer_in_bound;
```

